lead_paragraph: The Zika virus is overshadowing the final preparations for the Rio de Janeiro Olympics, even eclipsing concerns over deep budget cuts and severe water pollution.

headline.print_headline: Zika Virus Overshadows Buildup to Rio De Janeiro Olympics
